Female. Length 8.5 –10.0 mm. Similar to male. Apex of last ventrite truncate. Sternite VIII (
Fig. 25
) medially weakly sclerotized, apex truncate and slightly concave at middle, with dense extremely long setae along apical margin, spiculum long. Spermathecal receptaculum strongly swollen (
Fig. 32
), abruptly narrowed between receptaculum and pump, pump narrow and curved, spermathecal duct slightly projecting into receptaculum. Gonocoxae ( Figs 35, 36 ) separated, triangular, apex with one or two long setae.

